{
  "texts": [
    "We now present approaches in NLG.",
    "NLG deals with sequence-tosequence (seq2seq) tasks in NLP, which take a sequence as input and produce a sequence.",
    "Challenges in the presence of dialects in a generation task can differ significantly given the task.",
    "The data and evaluation methods can be different for tasks, especially where dialectal text is being generated.",
    "Some examples of such problems are summarisation, question answering and machine translation, and are described in Table 7."
  ]
}